        <section class="content-items-small">
            <h3>Opening Times</h3>
            <p>Zoo Bazaar is open every day of the year except for Christmas Day.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Winter season (September 1 - May 31): 9am - 5pm</li>
                <li>Summer season (June 1 - August 31): 10am - 6pm</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All outdoor animal exhibits will close one hour prior to the zoo's posted closing time, and all animals will be moved indoors to their enclosures at that time.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="content-items-small">
